summary: Throughout my 7 years of experience working in dynamic and result oriented environments I have successfully developed marketing strategies, executed creative marketing campaigns and managed client relationships with global brands. Being team work-oriented and driven with a go-getter attitude, I have effectively lead cross-functional teams, delivering impactful results to reach and engage target audiences, while specializing in creating engaging messaging and compelling content throughout traditional as well as digital marketing channels. Passionate about driving business success forward through measurable results in marketing, sales and outreach initiatives as well as devising creative strategies in teams, I thrive working in stimulating environments, where I can make a long lasting impact.
